  <h3 id="feature-surface">Feature Surface</h3>
  <p>
    What a workflow standard covers, and where each capability is fulfilled. <strong>Protocol</strong> =
    fixed by the Workflow contract (the only lock); <strong>Engine</strong> = resolved behind the swappable
    <code>CustomWorkflowEngine</code> provider; <strong>Compose</strong> = deferred to a neighbouring Web
    Everything standard.
  </p>
